Package fr.smart_builders.simulator.models.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFridgeEvent
    The abstract class AbstractFridgeEvent gives a common type for all fridge events normally there are three
    CloseDoorFridge
    The class CloseDoorFridge describes the event that the frdige's door is closed by the user
    OpenDoorFridge
    The class OpenDoorFridge describes the event that the fridge's door is opened by the user
    RunFridge
    The class RunFridge describes the event that the fridge starts running (if it is allowed to ) its cinsumtion goes to eco or normal mode consumption value depending on its mode at the running moment the fridge start running when its inner temperature is high
    StopFridge
    The class StopFridge describes the event that the fridge stops running, its consumption falls to a negligible value
    SwitchEcoFridge
    The class SwitchEcoFridge defines the event of the fridge mode set to eco to consume less.
    SwitchNormalFridge  
    SwitchOffFridge
    The class SwitchOffFridge defines the event of the fridge is not allowed to run
